ActIndian Act
SubjectMount Currie Indian Reserve No. 6 and Nesuch Indian Reserve No. 3 REVOCATION AND SURRENDER
PrecisOrder accepting a revocation of a surrender of certain minerals and surface rights on portions of Mount Currie Indian Reserve No. 6 and Nesuch Indian Reserve No. 3, in British Columbia, surrendered to Her Majesty in trust to lease or toherwise dispose of these rights.
